- [ ] PRODUCT_CARDS has 4 products with productType, productName, cardLabel fields
- [ ] PRODUCT_CARDS_OPTIONS maps productName to value (for select dropdowns)
- [ ] TProductType and TProductName types exported
- [ ] findProductBySlug helper exported
- [ ] getProductCardLabel uses productName (not productCard)
- [ ] app/api/agent/submit/route.ts updated to use new field name
